OL,7,FA Dumfries and Galloway congregation
OL,8,Fis fighting plans over a controversial
OL,9,Fdecision that will see a church's
OL,10,Fdoors permanently closed.
OL,12,FSouthwick Church, near , is set to
OL,13,Fclose in 2027 as part of plans by the
OL,14,FChurch of Scotland.
OL,16,FThe Church of Scotland state that they
OL,17,Fare "facing the double difficulty of
OL,18,Fdecreasing numbers of both ministers
OL,19,Fand congregational members."
