OL,7,FMark Jardine the Deputy Lord
OL,8,FLieutenant for The Stewartry, said:
OL,9,F"The church is in good condition and
OL,10,Fthere is a great congregation.
OL,12,F"I think this one should be spared but
OL,13,FI do feel sorry for the Church of ,
OL,14,Fthey have got some difficult decisions
OL,15,Fto make, but this is the wrong
OL,16,Fdecision here."
OL,18,FThe news of the closure has been met
OL,19,Fwith consternation amongst those who
OL,20,Fworship here and use its facilities.
