OL,4,CChurch of Scotland plans to close
OL,5,Clocal church
OL,7,F"We are aware of the close emotional
OL,8,Fties which people have with their
OL,9,Flocal church and we share in the
OL,10,Fsadness felt when decisions are made
OL,11,Fto release church buildings, but we
OL,12,Fbelieve radical reform is necessary to
OL,13,Fallow us to flourish in the future.
OL,15,F"Strong and effective mission, with a
OL,16,Fparticular focus on supporting the
OL,17,Fmost vulnerable people in society, is
OL,18,Fat the heart of what the church is
OL,19,Fabout and this work is not dependent
OL,20,Fon buildings.
