OL,3,C'The wrong decision' - Outrage as
OL,4,CChurch of Scotland plans to close
OL,5,Clocal church
OL,7,F"In this particular case, the South
OL,8,FWest Presbytery undertook the
OL,9,Fpreparation of a new Presbytery
OL,10,FMission Plan, as it was required to do
OL,11,Fby an Act of the General Assembly.
OL,13,F"Following the circulation of draft
OL,14,Fproposals representatives of every
OL,15,Fcongregation affected, including
OL,16,FSouthwick, were invited to meet with
OL,17,Fmembers of the Planning Committee in
OL,18,FDumfries.
