OL,3,C'The wrong decision' - Outrage as
OL,4,CChurch of Scotland plans to close
OL,5,Clocal church
OL,7,F"This was an opportunity to discuss
OL,8,Fthe draft recommendations and advance
OL,9,Farguments as to why the proposals
OL,10,Fshould be re-examined.
OL,12,F"Once the draft was finalised the
OL,13,FMission Plan was discussed and voted
OL,14,Fon by Presbytery, and, again, members
OL,15,Fof the congregations, including
OL,16,FSouthwick, were invited to that
OL,17,Fmeeting in order to present the case
OL,18,Ffor their building being retained.
