OL,3,C'The wrong decision' - Outrage as
OL,4,CChurch of Scotland plans to close
OL,5,Clocal church
OL,7,F"Following the decision being taken to
OL,8,Fapprove the new mission plan and close
OL,9,Fthis church there was then an
OL,10,Fopportunity for the matter to be
OL,11,Freviewed.
OL,13,F"Southwick applied for such a review,
OL,14,Fand submitted their arguments to the
OL,15,Fcommittee, which is independent of the
OL,16,FSouth West Presbytery.
OL,18,F"The review application was
OL,19,Funsuccessful, and the decision of the
OL,20,Fpresbytery to close this building in
OL,21,F2027 was upheld."
